Q1/- What are the limitations of EntityManager methods to perform CRUD operations with
     DB?
     
Answer:- Limitations of EntityManager:-

         1. Bulk updating and deleting of data is not possible,
         
         2. To access Entity object we can not specify some extra condition.
         
         3.Retrieving Entity object based on only ID field(Primary Key) i.e @ID annotation.
         
         4. Multiple Entity object retrieval is not possible (multiple record).